	   <tr><td colspan=2>I personally think halfling warriors are the best warriors out there.&nbsp;&nbsp;They A. have great starting stats, B. start in a friendly city, with the best newbie zone, C. can regen more than a troll with iksar cp on, and D. are the fastest leveling race/class combo in game.  They have a very nice balance of stats, and are small so you dont have to get shrunk all the time like the large races do.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
