	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, Sep 14th 8:55 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>INT is meaningless to warrior skills. Most offensive skills (1HS, 2HS, 1HB, 2HB, Slam/Bash, Kick) are STR dependent, not INT dependent. I have played halfling, troll, and ogre warriors, and tested each for speed of skill increase, and Abashi has confirmed these findings as well.<br><br>Piercing is DEX related.<br><br>I am unsure as to Offense (I assume STR) or Defense (AGI would make sense, but who knows in Verant's world).<br><br>My ogre gains skill the most quickly, by far, followed by my troll. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
