	   <tr><td colspan=2>I believe some of the above information is inaccurate.<br><br>Agility affects Armor Class (though not Armor Class increasing skills like Dodge or Parry).<br><br>Dexterity affects the frequency of BOTH Weapon Procs AND Critical Hits.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>-Ryltar Rilynt'tar<br>Druzzil Ro</td></tr>
