	   <tr><td colspan=2>AC is the main focus of a tank.&nbsp;&nbsp;However I accept some compromises in order to improve dex and agility.  I think part of this is what level you are.  As you get higher the mobs do more damage so AC becomes even more important.  However I have tried as a Barb Warrior to keep 100 agil and dex ( or near them lately...lol) and have always been amazed at how often I am just missed by mobs.  In regards to taunting I recommend the use of 2h weapons so your attacks get the mobs attentions.  This works for us large warriors and there are all sorts of variations.  There are many paths to the goal of being a good tank.  I hope I have added just a bit to this excellent post.<br><br>Skarp Njalson<br>"Circle of Three"<br>Povar <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
