	   <tr><td colspan=2>Never make an enemy of a cleric.<br><br>Seriously tho, clerics are your best friend. I don't hunt anywhere without a cleric.&nbsp;&nbsp;Ever see a druid try to heal 3200 hp's during battle?  Clerics CH is the best spell in the game.<br><br>Using CH means they won't get aggro'd either.  If your doing your warriorly duity, and have the mobs all whacking on you, then you should never have to pull a mob off anyone except an overnuking crunchie.<br><br>If a mob gets on a ranger or rogue, the clerics gonna have to heal them and they probably won't waste a CH, if Baddie isn't looking at you when that Sup Heal hits, its gonna be on your cleric.  Luckly, my pet cleric has 960+ AC so he can tank better than rangers, but I still don't think he appreciates the attention.<br>&nbsp;<br>Braun - 59ish Ogre Warrior<br>Torvonnilous</td></tr>
